response.original_title: The Making of ONE SHOT with Ed Sheeran: A Music Experience
response.overview: One singer. One city. One shot. Go behind the scenes with Ed Sheeran and Director Phil Barantini (Adolescence) as they rock the streets of New York with this groundbreaking, one take music experience.
response.title: The Making of ONE SHOT with Ed Sheeran: A Music Experience
